metadata.name: Drunken Vikings Tribe #1
metadata.description:
Drunken Vikings Tribe is a collection of 3636 NFTs sailing their way on the Ethereum blockchain.
The tribe sets sail, drunk and determined to conquer new lands. They gather more members as they explore new territories. One night, around the campfire, they realize their lives lack adventure. They decide to set out for Valhallaverse, but any outcome will do. They face unexpected challenges, like a damaged ship and navigation difficulties, but they press on. The true adventure, they discover, is the journey. They toast to the unexpected and to going beyond just getting drunk, but to the point of adventure.
